{"tid":505370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再有北韓士兵越過邊境 逃到南韓變節","createTime":"2017-12-21T04:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T12:22:32.000Z","uid":13663,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b9529b15c3e1152735a80186ebdf3cab65185528","tid":505370,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"再有北韓士兵變節，南韓國防部指，一名北韓士兵周四早上越過南北韓邊境非軍事區（DMZ）投奔南韓。<br />\n<br />\n國防部發言人指，變節的北韓士兵是基層人員，在當地時間周四早上8時04分(本港7時04分)，在濃霧中越過邊境逃到南韓。雙方未開一槍。這是五個星期內，第二宗同類事件。<br />\n<br />\n其後北韓士兵想接近兩韓邊境搜索該名變節士兵，南韓軍方隨即開大約20槍作警告。<br />\n<br />\n11月中一名北韓士兵越過休戰區兩韓邊境投奔南韓，北韓士兵猛烈開火阻止，他身中5槍受重傷，事發後北韓已撤換了板門店共同警備區的所有警備兵力。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社/路透社"},{"pid":"904ad900919e5aaf8d7161dfa65c7b97f1b85e4f","tid":505370,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d370cb9c009dc4c9f1e40237f48756c7cc2b008","tid":505370,"uid":135197,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"第一個走果個做咗榜樣?"},{"pid":"0ba9a716feedcea23e34fc53ac130a22d7664b52","tid":505370,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:54:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171221/1263372/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171221%2F1263372%2F&d=pLN3bEDIYDO9G7KjYHSZGwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=81f47209\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171221%2F1263372%2F&h=d7407a11\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171221/1263372/</a><br />\n<br />\n【更新】又有北韓士兵逃亡　濃霧中越過板門店到南韓"},{"pid":"dd54cec30ed76c1c271969a2321540273093c6d2","tid":505370,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB